  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It has two underscores to ensure it isn't overridden by any property from the search API in the future and that we don't override a real property (one underscore is reserved for the engine-internal response attributes, two therefore for InstantSearch).\n\nYou can safely use this property, it's not internal.\n\nI didn't know about the ~ for internal properties, could be useful in the future, but changing now would be breaking. automaticInsights for example comes from the search engine response directly",
